"title": "4203: earth, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4203",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Created and sustained by God, the world is both his possession and the dwelling-place of his creatures. As such, it should bring him glory, and will one day be judged by him.</p>\n<h2>God created the earth from nothing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:11\">EXO 20:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1-Gen1:2\">GEN 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:17\">EXO 31:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:15\">2KI 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:7\">JOB 26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:17\">PSA 74:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:15\">PSA 115:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:90\">PSA 119:90</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:24\">ISA 44:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:12\">ISA 45:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:13\">ISA 48:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:12\">JER 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:5\">JER 27:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:17\">JER 32:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:2\">JER 33:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:13\">AMO 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:24\">ACT 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:5\">2PE 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:6\">REV 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h2>The earth belongs to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:14\">DEU 10:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1\">PSA 24:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:4-Ps95:5\">PSA 95:4–95:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:29\">EXO 9:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:13\">JOS 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1SA 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11\">1CH 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:9\">PSA 47:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:11\">PSA 89:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:26\">1CO 10:26</a></p>\n<h2>God controls and sustains the earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:6-Ps135:7\">PSA 135:6–135:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:16-Gen9:17\">GEN 9:16–9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:10\">JOB 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:5\">JOB 28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13-Ps104:14\">PSA 104:13–104:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8\">PSA 147:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:25\">JER 33:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:3\">HOS 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:17\">COL 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's character seen on earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:11\">PSA 85:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:64\">PSA 119:64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:9\">ISA 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a></p>\n<h2>The earth should resound to God's glory and praise</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:1\">PSA 96:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:23\">ISA 44:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">PSA 47:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:4\">PSA 66:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:9\">PSA 72:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:5\">PSA 108:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:7\">PSA 148:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:13\">ISA 49:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:3\">HAB 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13\">REV 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>The earth is the habitation of human beings and the animals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:16\">PSA 115:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:22\">GEN 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26\">GEN 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28-Gen1:30\">GEN 1:28–1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:17\">GEN 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:1\">GEN 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></p>\n<h2>God judges the earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:14\">1CH 16:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:5\">NAM 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:22\">DEU 32:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:10\">1SA 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:16\">2SA 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:6\">JOB 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:6\">PSA 46:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:18\">PSA 77:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:21\">ISA 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:9\">ISA 26:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a></p>\n<h2>God will destroy the earth one day</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25-Ps102:26\">PSA 102:25–102:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10-2Pet3:12\">2PE 3:10–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:1-Isa24:6\">ISA 24:1–24:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:6\">ISA 51:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:23-Jer4:26\">JER 4:23–4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:35\">MAT 24:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:31\">MRK 13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:7\">2PE 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:11\">REV 20:11</a></p>\n<h2>God will create a new earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">ISA 66:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1\">REV 21:1</a></p>",
